    photoCredits: "Hero: Radosław Botev / CC BY 3.0 pl / (Wikimedia Commons). Gallery: Mehdi / Pexels License; Sami  Aksu / Pexels License; Zehra Rekibe Başol / Pexels License; Teomancimit / CC BY-SA 3.0 / (Wikimedia Commons); Creator:Rolfcosar / CC BY-SA 3.0 / (Wikimedia Commons); Rolf Cosar / CC BY-SA 4.0 / (Wikimedia Commons); TaylanOzgurUksal / CC BY-SA 4.0 / (Wikimedia Commons); Guérin Nicolas / CC BY-SA 3.0 / (Wikimedia Commons); German Archaeological Institute, photo E. Kücük. / CC BY 4.0 / (Wikimedia Commons); Dosseman / CC BY-SA 4.0 / (Wikimedia Commons); tobeytravels / CC BY-SA 4.0 / (Wikimedia Commons).",
